reauth_confirm.description:
Your Pluxee session expired. Open this link in your browser, log in again (email + captcha + one-time code), then paste the resulting `https://consumers.pluxee.at/oidc/callback?code=...` URL below.

{auth_url}

**Optional — stay logged in:** to avoid this in future, also paste the session cookie. In the same browser, press **F12 → Network**, click any request to `connect.pluxee.app`, open **Headers → Request Headers**, and copy the entire **`Cookie:`** value (it contains `op_session`; alternatively, paste the `op_session*` rows from the Application → Cookies tab).

